---
title: Thai-Style Tangy Chicken Noodle Stir-Fry 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: This flavorful noodle dish comes together in just 15 minutes—all in one pan! You'll stir-fry juicy dark meat chicken, then toss in ramen along with our tangy-sweet tamarind sauce and shredded cabbage and carrots. Finish with a big squeeze of lime juice, a drizzle of Sriracha, and a sprinkle of peanuts for crunchy contrast.
